  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of CIPRO XR Versus CIPRO IR in Patients With Complicated Urinary Tract Infections</brief_title>
  <acronym>EMERON</acronym>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of Ciprofloxacin Extended-Release 1000 mg Once-Daily Versus Ciprofloxacin Immediate-Release 500 mg Twice-Daily Given 7-14 Days in Patients With Complicated Urinary Tract Infections: Prospective, Randomized, Double-Blind Trial.</official_title>
